parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or lunge forward, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle surges or lunges forward when shifting into gear
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle jerks or shudders when shifting
the transmission warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause the vehicle to surge or lunge forward, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle surges or lunges forward when shifting into gear
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the throttle body warning light illuminates
the vehicle has a delayed or sudden acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or lunge forward, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the mechatronic unit can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission warning light illuminates
the vehicle surges or lunges forward when shifting into gear
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission slips or hesitates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration and surging of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle surges or accelerates on its own
especially when shifting into gear
braking
or reversing; the vehicle lurches or jumps forward or backward; the engine RPM increases suddenly; the vehicle accelerates without pressing the gas pedal.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body and sensor can cause unintended acceleration, loss of power, and stalling, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The throttle body and sensor malfunction
causing the vehicle to surge or accelerate unexpectedly; the vehicle hesitates or stalls; the engine RPM fluctuates; the vehicle's performance is affected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause sudden acceleration, jerking, or surging of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle surges or jerks forward or backward when taking foot off the brake
sudden acceleration without pressing the gas pedal
erratic idling
and stalling.
